data.description: Well maintained 2-story home on a beautiful, private lot with an assumable VA loan at 2.25%! As you step inside, you are greeted by beautiful engineered hardwood floors that lead into the living room where you can cozy up by the gas fireplace on chilly evenings. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances (refrigerator stays!), pantry, and coffee bar area. Upstairs you'll find three bedrooms, including the vaulted oversized primary suite which features a double sink vanity, walk-in shower, and walk-in closet. The laundry room is conveniently located upstairs, and the washer and dryer stay! Enjoy the privacy provided by the trees as you relax year round on the covered back patio. The yard is fully fenced and includes a built-in fire pit. With quick access to the river, park, and highway, this home is ideally located!
